sentences.english: This is the most famous, in the history of UFO, the "Roswell Incident".
sentences.chinese: 這就是不明飛行物史上最著名的“羅斯韋爾事件”。

sentences.english: Some of them are spaceships from outer space.
sentences.chinese: 有些不明飛行物是外太空來訪的太空船。

sentences.english: He had earlier claimed to have been shown round a UFO in 2001.
sentences.chinese: 他曾稱自己在2001年參觀過一個不明飛行物。

sentences.english: I disbelieved reports of UFO sightings.
sentences.chinese: 我不信關於見到不明飛行物的各種報道。

sentences.english: That's the same proportion who believe in unidentified flying objects.
sentences.chinese: 另有相同比例的人相信存在不明飛行物。

sentences.english: high-ranking officials have carefully covered up all the hard evidence of UFOs.
sentences.chinese: 高層官員已經細掩蓋了所有不明飛行物的確鑿證據。

sentences.english: Immediately report the event to a UFO research organization.
sentences.chinese: 馬上跟不明飛行物研究機構報告。
